# This directory is operator-guide only. Only docs/guide/ is tracked.
# Other files under docs/ (vision, roadmap, foundation contracts, AI
# session logs, founder release sign-off) are kept locally as working
# notes — they are not part of the published repo surface.
#
# The rule is enforced from the repo-root .gitignore:
#
#     /docs/*
#     !/docs/guide/
#     !/docs/.gitignore
#
# To add a new public document, put it under docs/guide/ or carve out
# an explicit exception above.
